code: /**  * Generate a key based on the specified parameters.  */ public static Object generateKey(Object... params) {     if (params.length == 0) {         return SimpleKey.EMPTY.     }     if (params.length == 1) {         Object param = params[0].         if (param != null && !param.getClass().isArray()) {             return param.         }     }     return new SimpleKey(params). }
